{"tid":376560,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【累人累物】男女10號風球下行飛鵝山被困   消防通宵營救同遇險","createTime":"2017-08-27T05:47:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-27T06:16:49.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0810843720a8a1b3f25ea7319885febef51a83f3","tid":376560,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T05:47:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/ee2e1287605268231a1641777187fd03\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2Fee2e1287605268231a1641777187fd03&h=df5c376b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n帕卡襲港下，一對男女昨日到黃大仙飛鵝山行山，至晚上7時47分，警方接報指2人被困山頭，於是聯同消防員等近百人登山拯救。至凌晨時份，首先將被困男子救出，由於出現低溫不適，需要送院。<br />\n<br />\n至於女事主因滑下百米深斜坡，腳部受傷，導致營救困難，消防小心翼翼游繩以下，陪伴在其身傍，但由於狂風大雨，山上環境惡劣，山路濕滑，未能將她救離險地，只能夠取來毛氈為她保暖，通宵陪伴在山頭，至早上8時許，山上的救援人員亦難抵一晚風雨，需要通知上峰增援，要求調派近百張毛氈到山上，供救援隊伍使用保暖。"},{"pid":"66c286245bf9e77d713ef629c854942af8f26996","tid":376560,"uid":23271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T05:59:20.000Z","msg":"10 號？<br />\n標題黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c56923f2d1380774de4a1ccb220be2f4628e4440","tid":376560,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T06:00:34.000Z","msg":"10號風球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdf53c7eae70c96a29d349166494b7f8689a9ab9","tid":376560,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T06:01:05.000Z","msg":"彩輝？"},{"pid":"9ce125c2c51d854e5961ae2ded5366a0e30b464d","tid":376560,"uid":116705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T06:06:57.000Z","msg":"正皮是給消防員的"},{"pid":"4ec894ab68f7c61b96c7702fa4532cb4ae7b5a54","tid":376560,"uid":1643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T06:16:49.000Z","msg":"琴日好好天喎，邊撚度 10 號"}]}